title: Uprooted, Ep. 6: Becoming a Wisconsinite
description: The Cubans who immigrated to the United States during the Mariel Boatlift have left Fort McCoy. Some found homes in Wisconsin and got jobs. Some started families. But first, they had to find sponsors.
